'''Amos Frimpong''' is an [[association football]]er who plays [[right back]] for [[Kumasi Asante Kotoko]] in the [[Ghana Premier League]]. He is currently the captain of the team.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ghanasportsonline.com/index.php/local-football-news/item/3913-exclusive-defender-amos-frimpong-named-permanent-skipper-of-asante-kotoko |title=Exclusive: Defender Amos Frimpong Named Permanent Skipper Of Asante Kotoko |date=3 March 2015 |website=GhanaSportsOnline.com}}</ref> Amos was bought to fill in for the departing of [[Yaw Frimpong]] to [[TP Mazembe]].
